  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Figgy Frogwich</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Figgy Frogwich</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meat\" title=\"Meat\">Meat</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> item exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i> and introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together/Version_History#Waterlogged_Beta_.28since_July_26.2C_2021.29\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together/Version History\">Waterlogged</a></i> beta. Consuming it will increase the player&#x27;s body temperature by 1 degree per second in 15 seconds.\n</p><p>Adding a Vegetable has a 50% chance to result in a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\">Froggle Bunwich</a>. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a> results in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Nuggets\" title=\"Honey Nuggets\">Honey Nuggets</a>. Using only one <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twig</a> will result in Kabobs. Adding one Twig and any piece of Meat (besides a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacles\" title=\"Barnacles\">Barnacle</a>) will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figkabab\" title=\"Figkabab\">Figkababs</a>. Using any <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Egg</a> and a Vegetable will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pierogi\" title=\"Pierogi\">Pierogi</a>. Using a Barnacle and a Vegetable will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacle_Pita\" title=\"Barnacle Pita\">Barnacle Pita</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figs\" title=\"Figs\"><img alt=\"Figs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Figs.png?a3500a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figgy_Frogwich\" title=\"Figgy Frogwich\"><img alt=\"Figgy Frogwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Figgy_Frogwich.png?1bfcb2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\"><a href=\"https:/