div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figs\" title=\"Figs\"><img alt=\"Figs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Figs.png?a3500a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figgy_Frogwich\" title=\"Figgy Frogwich\"><img alt=\"Figgy Frogwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Figgy_Frogwich.png?1bfcb2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>50% Chance to result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Froggle_Bunwich\" title=\"Froggle Bunwich\">Froggle Bunwich</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figs\" title=\"Figs\"><img alt=\"Figs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Figs.png?a3500a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Frog_Leg\" title=\"Frog Leg\"><img alt=\"Frog Leg.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Frog_Leg.png?1afed8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figgy_Frogwich\" title=\"Figgy Frogwich\"><img alt=\"Figgy Frogwich.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Figgy_Frogwich.png?1bfcb2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figgy_Frogwich#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Figgy_Frogwich#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
