  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|image = Figgy Frogwich Dropped.png\n|icon = Figgy Frogwich.png\n|foodType = [[Meats|Meat]] [[File:Meats.png|32px|]]\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Figs}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Frog Leg}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|spoil          = 15 Days\n|stack          = 40\n|hpRestored     = 20\n|hungerRestored = 25\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime       = 20 sec\n|priority       = 1\n|crafting       = Cooked in a [[Crock Pot]]\n|spawnCode      = \"frognewton\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = The fig really brings it all together.\n|willow = All that fig almost masks the frog flavor.\n|wolfgang = Is sweet, but also slimy.\n|wendy = Sweet and only a little slimy.\n|wx78 = READY FOR CONSUMPTION\n|wickerbottom = It has quite a unique flavor.\n|woodie = The fig masks the swamp taste.\n|maxwell = This recipe has legs.\n|wigfrid = Intö my belly with ye!\n|webber = Something we both like!\n|warly = A lesser known French recipe.\n|wormwood = Squishy\n|winona = Surprisingly tasty.\n|wortox = How do the mortals come up with these things?\n|wurt = Glurph! There frog leg in this!\n|walter = Hey, that's pretty good! What's in it?\n|wanda = It's very flavorful.\n|choose = wortox\n}}\n\n'''Figgy Frogwich''' is a [[Meat]] [[Food]] item exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'' and introduced in the ''[[Don't_Starve_Together/Version_History#Waterlogged_Beta_.28since_July_26.2C_2021.29|Waterlogged]]'' beta. Consuming it will increase the player's body temperature by 1 degree per second in 15 seconds.\n\nAdding a Vegetable has a 50% chance to result in a [[Froggle Bunwich]]. Adding [[Honey]] results in [[Honey Nuggets]]. Using only one [[Twigs|Twig]] will result in Kabobs. Adding one Twig and any piece of Meat (besides a [[Barnacles|Barnacle]]) will result in [[Figkabab|Figkababs]]. Using any [[Eggs|Egg]] and a Vegetable will result in [[Pierogi]]. Using a Barnacle and a Vegetable will result in [[Barnacle Pita]].\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Figs\n|item2 = Frog Leg\n|item3 = Filler\n|item4 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Figgy Frogwich\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Crock Pot}} Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Figs\n|item2 = Frog Leg\n|item3 = Twigs\n|item4 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Figgy Frogwich\n|note={{pic24|Prototype}} The most economical recipe\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Figs\n|item2=Frog Leg\n|item3=Twigs\n|item4=Vegetables\n|tool=Crock Pot\n|result=Figgy Frogwich\n|note=50% Chance to result in [[Froggle Bunwich]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1=Figs\n|item2=Frog Leg\n|item4=Berry\n|item3=Berry\n|tool=Crock Pot\n|result=Figgy Frogwich\n}}\n\n\n[[vi: Figgy Frogwich]]\n{{clear}}\n{{Crock Pot Food}}"
